{"tid":2259114,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"ON9我解到我男朋友Face Id","createTime":"2020-10-26T14:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T15:17:03.000Z","uid":302300,"like":8,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"40296acdc9320ef2fccbebac982379668864c397","tid":2259114,"uid":302300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:20:34.000Z","msg":"有一日，我屎窟痕開我男朋友手機睇。<br />\n開手機好正常咁向上拉，<br />\n我打左個突，仆街點解開到嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通佢係我訓教個陣用手機幫我整左個Face Id<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心諗好Sweet呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試多幾次確定咗諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「你幫我整左Face id咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「仆街！你點開到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「就咁照照就開到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「你包面到開到我手機，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">肥系</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「你女生男相呀，男人樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」<br />\n原來佢根本冇搞過，仆街仲等我開心左幾分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底係我肥，定有夫妻相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試多兩試，佢都開到我手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n減肥減埋個波都減唔到面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包面辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢米8 90肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我米65 50頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人發生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TAwztC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TAwztC.jpg&h=41dc974f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb69ee161db74f4ab7f887c03d709b25ded26867","tid":2259114,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"感建分"},{"pid":"c514daef2fd7f4764ae33c693b46114799d65185","tid":2259114,"uid":271857,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:24:47.000Z","msg":"FBI 應該請你。"},{"pid":"d1091b8a0a33da926b65bdee70c6117ead5d1f75","tid":2259114,"uid":91606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:25:53.000Z","msg":"趁你訓左覺faceid<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032faca06cea478a585bedbc2b805da4c4536a35","tid":2259114,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:27:51.000Z","msg":"唔關事，你係變種人"},{"pid":"fc48add083f569e1cf6002b3ec7fc9105fcf4561","tid":2259114,"uid":369075,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\">我諗你嘅情況同肥姐開Calvin Sun部電話差唔多</s